Surf_lascivious , by Roosta

This is a shotgun based combat map intended for up to 32 people. 

A map born in the wake of the_gloaming, I present surf_lascivious. This is what I would work on when I got bored or frustrated with the_gloaming, and ended up working out quite nicely. Enjoy!

Thanks:
